{"tid":2139698,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7 月成本港歷來最熱月份　酷熱日數達 20 天","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:40:58.000Z","uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a32ccb3b9a96c7aca3b0c5c1addd70cd0392915","tid":2139698,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"夏日熱辣辣，香港天文台今日（4 日）表示，今年 7 月天氣創下本港自 1884 年有紀錄以來多個最熱紀錄，包括全月最高平均氣溫破紀錄達 33.3&deg;C，酷熱日數達 20 天，也創單月最多紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n月平均最高溫度、月平均溫度、月平均最低溫度破紀錄<br />\n<br />\n較正常強的副熱帶高壓脊，於 7 月大部分時間持續影響華南，天文台指今年 7 月是 1884 年有紀錄以來最熱月份，月平均最高溫度 33.3&deg;C 、月平均氣溫 30.2&deg;C，月平均最低平均氣溫則為 28.3&deg;C，比較正常的數值分別多 1.9&deg;C、1.4&deg;C 及 1.5&deg;C，上述 3 項指標都破了天文台紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n雨量只有正常平均 1/3<br />\n<br />\n7 月下雨天也比正常少，全月總雨量只有 125.4 毫米，遠比平均正常數值的 376.5 毫米少。由 1 月至 7 月的累計降雨量也只有 1088.8 毫米，比正常 1,473.3 毫米少約 26%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/117143658_3127593020664649_7618260118850400547_o_xmK0Z_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F117143658_3127593020664649_7618260118850400547_o_xmK0Z_1200x0.jpg&h=2a697bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/7-%E6%9C%88%E6%88%90%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E7%86%B1%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BD-%E9%85%B7%E7%86%B1%E6%97%A5%E6%95%B8%E9%81%94-20-%E5%A4%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F7-%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E9%2585%25B7%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2581%2594-20-%25E5%25A4%25A9%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Ydxs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=ad5d700d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F7-%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E9%2585%25B7%25E7%25